Leisurely enjoy daytour in Malaysia's famous Batu Cave & Genting Highlands
Board on a sightseeing boat tour along poetic Chao Phraya River amid stunning Bangkok's skylines
Visit Northern Thailand's beautifully venerated temples in duo provinces of Chiang Mai and Chiang Rai
Take a close look and happily interact with giant friends in Chiang Mai's elephant village
Spend time walking through quain and picturesque sites in Chiang Mai & Chiang Rai's exotic hill tribe villages
